00:17:49,669 --> 00:17:53,372
I think the duck has
more savoriness than chicken.

334
00:17:54,173 --> 00:17:55,808
The duck fat is good.

335
00:17:56,809 --> 00:18:00,980
The pieces that have a lot of fat

336
00:18:01,814 --> 00:18:02,782
