00:18:47,727 --> 00:18:48,961
He's making me want to try it.

345
00:18:50,529 --> 00:18:52,264
The oil from the duck is good.

346
00:18:59,305 --> 00:19:01,040
It's good.

347
00:19:01,107 --> 00:19:04,777
It’s good as is, certainly,

348
00:19:04,844 --> 00:19:09,582
