349
00:19:10,182 --> 00:19:11,984
Sir, one bowl of spicy noodles, please.

350
00:19:12,051 --> 00:19:14,053
-Sure.
-In Korea,

351
00:19:14,654 --> 00:19:17,923
do they not have noodles

352
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:21,494
